{"tid":1061344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"SOD情人節全新企劃！AV女優陪你一起「用愛發電」","createTime":"2019-03-14T10:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T12:30:28.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"868ac266b0b4da9cf4c86c0f5128fafde7f9242b","tid":1061344,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:33:22.000Z","msg":"日本AV製作公司 SOD將在明（14）日白色情人節舉辦新企畫，將請處男到「魔鏡號」裡，與AV女優一起「用愛發電」。讓沒有女友的男生們，也能享受情人節的浪漫。<br />\n <br />\nSOD將準備2台腳踏車，並讓參與的男性戴上VR裝置，將播放「帶來能源的影片」，而如要繼續看下去，則要不斷的踩腳踏車。剩餘的電會幫忙點亮浪漫的「愛心電燈」，<br />\n真的是名副其實的「用愛發電」。<br />\n <br />\n活動將在明日下午 5時於東京澀谷舉辦，現場除了開放一般參加以外，也請來了AV女優七海ティナ和小泉ひなた兩位到場。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BPwB30K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBPwB30K.png&h=868a57ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M3kjhkL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM3kjhkL.png&h=ed5c3068&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5450ed79f42233faed6d1d4183e8704523d93a8c","tid":1061344,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:48:42.000Z","msg":"以為係用光速屌西舞 將kinetic energy 轉為電能添"},{"pid":"85a3b77bbb87a1d43054d48ee3b71684060992ba","tid":1061344,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:04:37.000Z","msg":"劇烈運動加咸片刺激，究竟啲血會去邊度先呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"286c413ceec6404126f646021477f1944f165f2b","tid":1061344,"uid":21394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:23:16.000Z","msg":"睇AV唔番屋企睇，要踩住單車先有得睇，ON撚9。"},{"pid":"79b15915f3c86ca07472a6fa640f7f1e5957fd7e","tid":1061344,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T12:30:28.000Z","msg":"想係香港整部魔鏡號出租。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}